title: Rock Me Amadeus Cigars... Censored!
itunes:title: Rock Me Amadeus Cigars... Censored!
description: Junior Dominguez owner of Recluse Cigars joins us with his new release Recluse Cigars E.L.F. (Eight Legged Freak) Sidewinder and Kanu Packs as we light up The Recluse OTG, Recluse Draconian and the all new Recluse Amadeus. Cigar Geek and newest addition to The Cigar Authority Barry Stein joins us go "uncensored" this week on The Cigar Authority!
